	fixed typo.
	
2006-03-31  Daniel Stone  <daniel@freedesktop.org>

	* configure.ac:
	* Xprint/Makefile.am:
	* Xprint/ps/Makefile.am:
	* Xprint/ps/psout_ftpstype3.c:
	Add full FreeType support for Xprint.  (Drew Parsons)

